OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,FPolice are treating the latest arson
OL,7,Fattack in north-west London as an
OL,8,Fantisemitic hate crime.
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police say they have
OL,11,Fincreased resources around the area,
OL,12,Ffollowing a "series of arson and
OL,13,Fattempted arson attacks in north west
OL,14,FLondon."
OL,16,FMembers of the Jewish community have
OL,17,Fbeen urged to "remain calm" as counter-
OL,18,Fterror police investigate it alongside
OL,19,Fa series of similar incidents.
OL,26,@yD@OOUyD@[O]
