CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776615077
OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,FThere have been "online claims of
OL,7,Fresponsibility" for the arson and
OL,8,Fattempted arson attacks, said the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police, which is
OL,10,Fsupporting Counter Terrorism Policing
OL,11,F(CTP) London's investigation.
OL,13,FA man was spotted on Friday evening
OL,14,Fapproaching a row of shops carrying a
OL,15,Fplastic bag later found to contain
OL,16,Fthree bottles of fluid, the
OL,17,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,26,@nD@QOUoD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776615077
OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,FHe placed the bag by the former site
OL,7,Fof a Jewish charity "Jewish futures"
OL,8,Fin Hendon, Barnet, before lighting the
OL,9,Fitems inside.
OL,11,FThe man fled the scene when the
OL,12,Fbottles failed to fully ignite, the
OL,13,Fforce said, adding that the shopfront
OL,14,Fsustained minor damage and no injuries
OL,15,Fwere reported.
OL,17,FNo arrests have been made.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
