PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776615077
OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,FA police cordon was in place around a
OL,7,Fbuilding, said to be formerly used by
OL,8,Fthe Jewish community, on Saturday
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,11,FArmed response vehicles, CTP resources
OL,12,Fand police motorbikes have been
OL,13,Fdeployed to the area.
OL,15,FA "significantly increased" number of
OL,16,Funiformed and plain clothed Met
OL,17,Fofficers will be visible through the
OL,18,Fweekend and extra stop and search
OL,19,Fpowers have been granted across Barnet.
OL,26,@wD@COUwD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
