PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776615077
OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Luke
OL,7,FWilliams, who leads policing in the
OL,8,Farea, said:
OL,10,F"We continue to work with our
OL,11,Fcolleagues from Counter Terrorism
OL,12,FPolicing who are leading the
OL,13,Finvestigations into all of these
OL,14,Fincidents due to the similar
OL,15,Fcircumstances and online claims of
OL,16,Fresponsibility."
OL,18,FA spokesperson for the Community
OL,19,FSecurity Trust (CST), a British
OL,20,Fcharity working to provide safety to
OL,21,Fthe Jewish community, said:
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776615077
OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,F"We are aware of what appears to be
OL,7,Fanother attempted arson, this time
OL,8,Ftargeting a premises in north London
OL,9,Fpreviously used by the Jewish
OL,10,Fcommunity."
OL,12,FThe group said it is working to assist
OL,13,Fthe police investigation, adding:
OL,15,F"We urge people to remain calm and to
OL,16,Freport any suspicious activity, at any
OL,17,Ftime of day or night, to police
OL,18,Fimmediately on 999 and then to CST."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]wD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
