PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776615077
OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,FThe Campaign Against Antisemitism
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is yet another arson
OL,8,Fattack which appears to be targeting
OL,9,Fthe Jewish community ` it is the third
OL,10,Fin a month as we witness a worldwide
OL,11,Fpattern of attacks.
OL,13,F"It is unclear to what extent, if any,
OL,14,Fthey are being co-ordinated.
OL,16,F"Police have only just reopened a
OL,17,Fcentral London park over a drone
OL,18,Fthreat.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
