FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776615077
OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,F"Britain is under attack and those
OL,7,Fresponsible will not stop at targeting
OL,8,FJews.
OL,10,F"Meanwhile, the Government thinks it
OL,11,Fis 'not appropriate' to proscribe
OL,12,FIran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,13,FCorps."
OL,15,FIt is not being treated as a terrorist
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,FPolice and fire crews were called to
OL,19,Fthe scene on Friday night.
OL,26,@uD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
