PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776615077
OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,FCommander Helen Flanagan, of CTP
OL,7,FLondon, said earlier on Saturday:
OL,9,F"At this stage last night's arson is
OL,10,Fnot being linked to other incidents in
OL,11,Fthe north-west London area over the
OL,12,Flast week or last month's arson in
OL,13,FGolders Green, but counter-terrorism
OL,14,Fofficers are leading due to the
OL,15,Fsimilarities of each attack.
OL,17,F"I would ask that anyone with
OL,18,Finformation or footage that could help
OL,19,Four investigation gets in touch with
OL,20,Fpolice as soon as possible.
OL,26,@qD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
