OL,3,CLatest north-west London arson attack
OL,4,Cprobed as antisemitic hate crime
OL,6,F"We will be relentless in our pursuit
OL,7,Fof those responsible for this and
OL,8,Fother, similar, hateful acts against
OL,9,FLondon's communities."
